atg.commerce.order
Interface PipelineConstants

All Known Subinterfaces:
ApprovalConstants, B2BPipelineConstants
public interface PipelineConstants

This interface contains the Pipeline parameter constants. These constants are used for calling into the pipeline chains and passing parameters. Also, some of the constants are used for extracting data from the PipelineResult object.

See Also:
PipelineResult
